Source:  Ohinemuri Gazette
Author:
Vol / Page:  2
Edition:
Quote:  The secretary of the Maoriland Mine at Waitekauri, received the following telegram from the mine manager on Saturday, the 13th:- "No. 3 level: Winze Young New Zealand Reef battery head sample from ore from winze for week, GBP11 per ton.  Width of ore exposed, 5ft."
